<p>I completely agree with Fer. Clerics cannot tank in the game at higher levels. I am level a level 66 cleric on Drinal server and while I have 5khp, and 170defense, I cannot tank anything higher than Bloodfields, and even then I can only take the level 50's in the zone. However, I do frequently melee, and do pretty good dps, so clerics can still melee and do good damage at it, especially with the 75-150dmg proc almost every hit with the summoned hammer. However, before level 50 I could tank but thats only because SOE was nice enough to keep the player to monster hp somewhat even, but after that they intend for you to sit down and heal the people.</p>
