<p>hmmmmm <br /> <br />so tanking for groups when needed means i am not a tank? <br />when can't find a tank for a DoN, and i tank the entire thing means i am not a tank? <br /> <br />just what is a tank then? <br /> <br />i already stated that i can't tank raid mobs. but exp groups that need a tank? i can fill that spot just fine. but to you thats not tanking? <br /> <br />/boggle <br /> <br />i guess your definition of a tank differs from mine. <br /> <br />the same case could be made for rangers, they arn't tanks, yet i have grouped with plenty that can tank. <br /> <br />same with monks...... <br />same with BLs...... <br /> <br /> <br />i guess i am not a &quot;tank&quot; but i can tank <br /> <br />lol <br /> <br />as far as tanking multiples, i can do that as well. it is amazing what paying attention to incoming pulls can do. i can have multiples under control before they reach camp, things that a warrior cannot do.  <br /> <br />when i tank, i do not just sit there and wait for the mob to get to me, if i did that, i would never have enough aggro to hold it. before it ever gets to camp i have already MoB/Mor, and stun it just as it reaches camp. that gives the slower time to slow, and also gives me decent aggro, then, i will stunn it again just as the first stunn wears off. then i have a 3rd stunn ready just incase i haven't pissed it off enough (SCS has made tanking more difficult, now i have to stunn alot more)and soon after my first stunn is now ready to go as well.  <br /> <br />if there are multiples, i will stunn one and root it. then stun another , then mor/mob then switch back to the first mob and stun it again, to be sure it wants me. then i will alternate betweent he two mobs, re rooting (even if it hasn't dropped yet)and stunning as nessesary. <br /> <br />but i guess that isn't tanking, what is it called then? clericing? <br /> <br />not..... <br /> <br />enchanting? <br /> <br />not..... <br /> <br />my guess would be tanking. <br /> <br />clerics IMO are one of the most well rounded classes in the game. <br /> <br />we can pull, we can CC, we can tank, we can now solo, and OMG we can heal too!!!! <br /> <br />oh wait! now your going to tell me we arn't pullers too.... <br /> <br />;-P</p>
